snippet.title: Living Books: Arthur's Teacher Trouble Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Living Books: Arthur's Teacher Trouble at School
Full Playthrough

Living Books: Arthur's Teacher Trouble is a game created by Broderbund Software in 1992. It s the second Living Books game and the first of the five Arthur Living Books games (including D.W. the Picky Eater) based on the 1986 storybook of the same name written by Marc Brown.
